snippet.title: This game is a childhood DREAM come true..
snippet.description:
Just wow. HOW did I not know about this game?! It's perfect while we all wait for MW2 to drop. Hyper Charge: Unboxed is such a stunning looking game and plays so well. 

Get the game here: (20% OFF THIS FRIDAY!) https://store.steampowered.com/app/523660/HYPERCHARGE_Unboxed/
